ModMetaData.description: A code library for user-customizable deep-filter searching of all things on the map. (This is the dev version of TD Find Lib. The release version of About.xml is available for editing at About/About-Release.xml. Edits made on this file or on the temporary About/About.xml won't show up on the release version. Use VisualStudio to build a "Release" version of this mod when ready to upload your mod!)
